    <item>
      <title>Iconiq Growth 在 ServiceTitan 首次公开募股中筹资逾 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/iconiq-growth-gains-more-than-1-billion-in-servicetitan-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，科技初创公司 ServiceTitan Inc. 本周在公开市场首次亮相，为早期投资者带来了巨额收益 - Iconiq Growth 获得了超过 10 亿美元的回报，Bessemer Venture Partners 获得了超过 8 亿美元的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/iconiq-growth-gains-more-than-1-billion-in-servicetitan-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 01:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Saylor 的 MicroStrategy 再次获纳斯达克 100 指数成分股青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/microstrategy-palantir-added-to-nasdaq-100-moderna-removed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克 100 指数的监管机构周五表示，互联网时代的软件制造商 MicroStrategy Inc. 将加入该指数，该公司转型为比特币杠杆押注者，令华尔街为之震惊。软件公司 Palantir Technologies Inc. 和泰瑟枪和警用随身摄像头制造商 Axon Enterprise Inc. 也将被加入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/microstrategy-palantir-added-to-nasdaq-100-moderna-removed</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 01:25:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的投资者为巴西零售业合并奠定基础</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/distressed-investor-lays-groundwork-for-brazil-retail-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，巴西资深商人 Nelson Tanure 同意收购杂货连锁店 Dia，并正在向反垄断监管机构试探其与竞争对手连锁店 Pao de Açucar 合并的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/distressed-investor-lays-groundwork-for-brazil-retail-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 23:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
