      <title>政治危机危及财政，法国信用评级遭下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/france-downgraded-by-moody-s-after-le-pen-derails-deficit-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞因预算纠纷推翻前任总理后，穆迪评级下调了法国的信用评级，对新政府施加压力，要求其控制不断膨胀的赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/france-downgraded-by-moody-s-after-le-pen-derails-deficit-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 23:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪因财政和政治风险下调斯洛伐克信用评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/slovakia-s-rating-cut-at-moody-s-on-fiscal-and-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将斯洛伐克的主权信用评分下调了一个等级，理由是担心政治紧张局势和国家债务恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/slovakia-s-rating-cut-at-moody-s-on-fiscal-and-political-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 21:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
